    <item>
      <title>科学家正在探索是否为飓风添加“6 类”名称</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/02/06/1229440080/scientists-explore-whether-to-add-a-category-6-designation-for-hurricanes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[气候变化使强飓风变得更加常见。一项新的研究表明，这可能需要为更强烈的风暴添加新的官方名称。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/02/06/1229440080/scientists-explore-whether-to-add-a-category-6-designation-for-hurricanes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:21:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会因边境和国家安全资金问题陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/02/06/1229490663/congress-devolves-into-chaos-over-border-and-national-security-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过几个月的争吵，国会仍然完全无法就任何有关边境安全或向以色列和乌克兰提供援助的立法达成一致——大多数立法者同意的所有优先事项都是必要的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/02/06/1229490663/congress-devolves-into-chaos-over-border-and-national-security-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:00:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《华尔街日报》专栏称密歇根市为“美国圣战之都”后，密歇根市加强了安全措施</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/02/06/1229437685/dearborn-wsj-arab-americans-jihad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》一篇专栏文章的影响导致密歇根州迪尔伯恩市市长增加了警力。自以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，仇恨犯罪有所增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/02/06/1229437685/dearborn-wsj-arab-americans-jihad</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:43:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
